data.description: Don't miss this one! This beautiful 4 bed, 2.5 bath, 2,040 sqft home is ideal for your growing family. The home has been lovingly maintained and tastefully updated. A wonderful home with the added benefit of being located a short distance to desired schools including George McParland Elementary School & East Union High School. New solid flooring has been installed and some of the many updates include the master bathroom, family bathroom and half bath. Gather around the 2 cozy fireplaces. The stunning kitchen features stainless steel appliances and display cupboards for a refined touch. Keep family and friends entertained for hours relaxing in the beautiful backyard featuring a covered patio and sparking pool.
